    <string name="blur_colors_notice">What are these colors doing?</string>
    <string name="blur_colors_notice_summary">These colors are the ones tiniting the BlurBackground. Instead of the normal Grey, you can now choose the colors in the way you like.\nThere are three color filters: One used for light backgrounds, one used for Dark backgrounds and one used for light/dark backgrounds.\nSo how these colors work?\nSimple, as the titles say, the Light filter will be used for Lighter backgrounds, Dark filter for dark backgrounds and the mixed filter one will be used for backgrounds not too dark but neither too light.\nThese colors are used for both BlurBackgrounds: StatusBar and RecentsApps window</string>
